                <h1>Montana Background Check Laws: What You Need to Know</h1>
                <p>Montana's background check laws require certain checks for firearm purchases. Federal law mandates checks through the National Instant Criminal Background Check System (NICS) for commercial sales, while private sales often do not require them. Understanding these laws is crucial for both buyers and sellers to ensure compliance and public safety.</p>
